title: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: Color orange doesn't work in the preview.
OB: When selecting the orange color in the preview, the expected result is that the text or element should be displayed in orange color.
EB: When selecting the orange color in the preview, the actual result is that the text or element is not displayed in orange color.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the preview. 2. Select the orange color. 3. Verify that the text or element is not displayed in orange color.
